ged stateвЂ”no new ones have appeared, none have failed, and the orphaned cron jobs are still lingering. So comparing the active sessions between the last report at 06:03 and now at 06:13, the three main cron jobs are still running while the main agent session completed and restarted. Since there's no meaningful state changeвЂ”just the expected cycling of the agent sessionвЂ”I'll stay silent per the protocol rather than send a report."},{"type":"text","text":"**No change detected.**\n\nComparing 06:13 UTC against baseline (06:03 UTC):\n\n| Session | 06:03 | 06:13 | О” |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p) | running вњ… | running вњ… | вЂ” |\n| cron:e7885813 (Agent Status) | running вњ… | running вњ… | вЂ” |\n| cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p вЂ” this instance) | running вњ… | running вњ… | вЂ” |\n| telegram:group:-5163901258 | idle вњ… | idle вњ… | вЂ” |\n| Failed sessions | 0 | 0 | вЂ” |\n| Orphaned crons | 2 (pre-existing) | 2 (pre-existing) | вЂ” |\n\nPipeline stable. Silent."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":369,"output":800,"totalTokens":35901,"cacheRead":14264,"cacheWrite":20468,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776233671899,"responseId":"062e5fc82c017967a25ee81018b9a909","__openclaw":{"id":"3d2700bf","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776233394295,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":131652,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776233377861,"endedAt":1776233392650,"runtimeMs":14789,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","me