-04-15 in local time, but it's currently April 14 23:16 UTC = April 15 06:16 UTC+7):\n\n\nQLHV backend has a merge request pending Lead review, while AHV Works still needs P0 fixes and the Stitch MCP wrapper test plus stitch-connect skill update remain on the backlog. The pipeline is running clean with no active subagents, and both the DTLX backend and frontend are stable, though there's no current blocker aside from the QLHV BE MR awaiting review."},{"type":"text","text":"**DAILY BRIEFING вЂ” Orbis рџЊђ**\nрџ“… Tuesday, April 15, 2026 вЂ” 06:16 AM (UTC+7)\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n**STATUS: вњ… HEALTHY**\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n---\n\n**в‘  YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED (Apr 14)**\n\n| # | Task | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 | DTLX BE Fix вЂ” `docs` vs `data` field mismatch | вњ… Fixed across all modules |\n| 2 | DTLX API Verification вЂ” 18/18 endpoints tested | вњ… All passing |\n| 3 | Pipeline Recovery вЂ” gateway timeout & Telegram delivery | вњ… HEALTHY restored |\n| 4 | Session Cleanup вЂ” prior abort instances cleared | вњ… Clean state |\n| 5 | Students page filter bug | вњ… Fixed |\n| 6 | Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) | вњ… Running stable |\n\n---\n\n**в‘Ў TODAY'S PRIORITIES (Apr 15)**\n\n| Priority | Task | Owner |\n|---|---|---|\n| рџ”ґ P0 | QLHV BE MR !6 вЂ” Lead review + merge | Lead |\n| рџџЎ P1 | AHV Works вЂ” 13 P0 issues pending fix | Agent queue |\n| рџџЎ P1 | Stitch MCP wrapper test | Agent queue |\n| рџџЎ P1 | Update stitch-connect skill | Agent queue |\n\n---\n\n**в‘ў BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n| Item | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Telegram delivery (17:40 UTC Apr 14) | вњ… Stable вЂ” no current issues |\n| QLHV BE MR !6 awaiting review | вЏі Pending Lead action |\n| No active subagents | вњ… Zero overhead |\n\n---\n\n**System Summary:**\n- DTLX BE: Running port 5555 вњ…\n- DTLX FE: Running port 3000 вњ…\n- Pipeline: HEALTHY вњ…\n- Active agents: 0\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”